        <section class="section3x9m2k" id="services4x8m2k">
            <h2>Comprehensive Handyman Services</h2>
            <p>At DecorXHub, we understand that maintaining your home requires expertise across multiple disciplines. Our team of skilled professionals brings years of experience to handle everything from minor repairs to major renovations. We pride ourselves on delivering quality workmanship that stands the test of time.</p>
            
            <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/5691551/pexels-photo-5691551.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800" alt="Handyman working" class="image-embed3k9m7x">
            
            <div class="grid4p7k2m">
                <div class="card8x3n5p">
                    <h4>Plumbing Solutions</h4>
                    <p>From leaky faucets to complete pipe replacements, our plumbing experts handle water-related issues with precision. We diagnose problems quickly and implement lasting solutions that prevent future complications. Whether it's a dripping tap keeping you awake at night or a complete bathroom renovation, we've got the tools and knowledge to get it done right.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="card8x3n5p">
                    <h4>Electrical Work</h4>
                    <p>Safety is paramount when dealing with electrical systems. Our certified electricians perform installations, repairs, and upgrades following strict safety protocols. We handle everything from simple outlet replacements to complex wiring projects, ensuring your home's electrical system operates efficiently and safely.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="card8x3n5p">
                    <h4>Carpentry & Woodwork</h4>
                    <p>Transform your space with custom carpentry solutions. Our craftsmen create beautiful, functional pieces from shelving units to complete deck installations. We work with various wood types and finishes to match your existing decor while ensuring structural integrity and longevity.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="card8x3n5p">
                    <h4>Painting & Finishing</h4>
                    <p>A fresh coat of paint can completely transform any room. Our painting specialists prepare surfaces meticulously and apply finishes with attention to detail. We use quality materials that provide excellent coverage and durability, whether you're refreshing a single room or repainting your entire home.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="card8x3n5p">
                    <h4>Drywall Repair</h4>
                    <p>Holes, cracks, and water damage don't stand a chance against our drywall experts. We seamlessly repair and restore walls to their original condition, matching textures and preparing surfaces for painting. Our repairs are virtually invisible once completed.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="card8x3n5p">
                    <h4>Flooring Installation</h4>
                    <p>Whether you prefer hardwood, laminate, tile, or vinyl, our flooring specialists install with precision. We ensure proper subfloor preparation, accurate measurements, and professional installation techniques that result in beautiful, long-lasting floors.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="highlight-box4m8k3x">
                <strong>Ready to get started?</strong> Our team is standing by to discuss your project needs. <a href="#contact8k3m9p" class="continue-btn7k3m9x">Click Here to Continue</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section3x9m2k" id="about7m3k9x">
            <h2>About DecorXHub</h2>
