                    <h3>2014 - Specialization Development</h3>
                    <p>Recognizing that excellence requires focus, we organized our team into specialized divisions. Electricians, plumbers, carpenters, and painters each developed their expertise while maintaining the collaborative spirit that defines DecorXHub. This structure allowed us to take on more complex projects while maintaining our commitment to quality.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="timeline-item2k8p4x">
                    <h3>2017 - Technology Integration</h3>
                    <p>We embraced modern technology to improve our service delivery. Online scheduling, digital project tracking, and enhanced communication tools made it easier for clients to work with us. We also invested in advanced diagnostic equipment that helps us identify problems more accurately and develop more effective solutions.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="timeline-item2k8p4x">
